item.title: Defyboys Cache Extractor
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

ffs FAT32 can only handle 32,767 files in a directory.
How many models are there?
42k - guess it crashes then!!! we’re not all on ntfs.

The only other problem i found is that the ends of the npc and item files seem screwed up, they probably changed the encryption just to thwart defyboy

Last readable entries are
Amulet of farming(8)
Ogleroot
Flag

Should give you a date to work from.

Read full topic
